9-09T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"40億？80億？你坐時光機黎架，宜家中零頭都唔只啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐時光機番你老母個閪到再投過胎唔好做香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f2e3ae394744410aff5c6b23851f7034c5cb7f","tid":1555624,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"數據中心最大弱點應該係電力"},{"pid":"d97b126276f421c63f511eb9d293c31573ea437d","tid":1555624,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b18733ccebda52a7deabff679884282edee3bfb9","tid":1555624,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"發覺間唔中就會有人開POST想叫人搞港交所，都費撚事解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐左幾耐<br />\n要搞不如去中大搞真正春袋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"中大個個係連登仔春袋囉 白痴"},{"pid":"3330befb7f99178409971187d06d686de8644fa4","tid":1555624,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97b126276f421c63f511eb9d293c31573ea437d","tid":1555624,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b18733ccebda52a7deabff679884282edee3bfb9","tid":1555624,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"發覺間唔中就會有人開POST想叫人搞港交所，都費撚事解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐左幾耐<br />\n要搞不如去中大搞真正春袋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"中大個個係連登仔春袋囉 白痴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"係香港春袋...<br />\n<br />\nPush <br />\n建議呢個星期全力<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂香港</span><br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但請起返連儂香港<br />\n唔係衝擊或散水或轉場，<span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n0. 幫襯良心小店<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BuvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=dea24064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"44ff56fb5f97de49303657e081414e6f91fc833a","tid":1555624,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97b126276f421c63f511eb9d293c31573ea437d","tid":1555624,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b18733ccebda52a7deabff679884282edee3bfb9","tid":1555624,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"發覺間唔中就會有人開POST想叫人搞港交所，都費撚事解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐左幾耐<br />\n要搞不如去中大搞真正春袋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"中大個個係連登仔春袋囉 白痴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐<im